hopobject.body: Excellent work, Nice Design datahealthusa.com The distraught mother also accused her ex-husband of not spending time at the hospital with their son (Usher's lawyer said he'd been spending all of his time there), and said that her ex-husband does not keep her informed of details of the boys' day-to-day lives. (The two also have a second son, Naviyd, 4.) She also said he failed to give her basic information about the accident after it happened.
